data.description: Are you looking for a peaceful sanctuary? Look no further! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch that sits on two parcels totaling 5.18 acres is the perfect place for you to call home.  With the possibility of a 4th bedroom, this home offers plenty of space for you and your family. The living room and great room provide ample space for relaxation and entertainment.  But that's not all! Our home also features a heated detached garage with concrete floors, perfect for storing your vehicles or using as a workshop.  And let's not forget about the stunning scenery that surrounds the home. Situated in a secluded area, you'll be surrounded by nature and all its beauty.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this home yours.
